com.paypal.selion.pojos

Class SeLionGridConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.pojos.SeLionGridConstants

  • public class SeLionGridConstants
extends Object
    A Class which contains String constants used throughout SeLion Grid Patterns & conventions used in naming the constants for this class

    - Anything that is a *DIR* ends with a '/'
    - Anything that is a *FILE* is a file
    - Anything that is a *URL* is relative to http://{hostname}:{port}
    - Anything that is a *RESOURCE* is a jar resource that can be loaded via the CLASSPATH
    - Anything that is a *PAGE* is a HTML page
    - Anything that is a *ARG* is a program argument
    - Any single constant may utilize more than one of these patterns/conventions
